dct_description_sm: a Rto. Bonne ; Bonne fil. del. ; André sculp.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
6 bar scales on map given in "Stadia olympica", "Milliaria judaica", "Milliaria romana", "Leucae francicae", "Parasangae persieae", Sehæni aegiptiaei".
Shows topography, drainage, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Appears in Desmarest's Atlas encyclopédique, Paris, 1787-8, No. 3.
